Text: Thank you for all your hard work, I greatly appreciate it. I was wondering if you can get the Ozzy Ozborn Book, Trust Me, I'm Dr. Ozzy: Advice from Rock's Ultimate Survivor. I would greatly appreciate it. I would also like to see the new Ellen Degenerous Book, I think I have seen it uploaded but not on epub. Once again Thank you for all your work, it is greatly appreciated.
You are my hero. Thanks so much
